data.description: Move in ready Club West townhome! Ideal end unit location on a quiet dead-end street. You will enjoy amazing features here such as the huge upper-level loft, primary bedroom with an ensuite bath + walk-in closet, 2 car attached garage, stainless steel appliances, and upper-level laundry. Easy living here with the HOA covering lawn/snow, building exterior, trash, and your water bill! Amenities include tennis courts, exercise room, pool, playground, and community room for hosting gatherings. Incredible location minutes from shopping, restaurants, entertainment, National Sports Center, TPC Golf Course, and Highway 10. You don't want to miss out on this one. Book a showing today!
